snippet.title: When a Desi Visits Singapore
snippet.description:
Singapore, saare desi parivaro ka family trip destination dekh aaye!

We saw - the Merlion, Singapore flyer, Marina bay sands hotel, skyline luge, checked out Changi airport, jewel changi, went on duck tours, slingshot, night safari, saw the beautiful gardens by the bay and Singapore super trees, flower dome and cloud forest. 

Use our code SLAYY10 on Headout to get 10% discount on all Singapore experiences - https://bit.ly/489gJrH

snippet.description:

►Song - Kuware Rahab

►Lyrics - Ashutosh Tiwari
►Music Director - Arya Sharma 
►Company/ Label - Wave Music

♪ Gaana : https://gaana.com/song/kuware-rahab
♪ Jio Saavn : https://www.jiosaavn.com/album/kuware-rahab/qR9HIFMiDT0_
♪ Wynk : https://wynk.in/u/lB8D1tkA2
♪ Watch To Earn on FanTV - https://fantv.in/watch/video-neelkamal-singh-shilpi-raj-kuware-rahab-vn4cMI
♪ Apple Music : https://music.apple.com/us/album/kuware-rahab-single/1722927815
♪ Amazon Prime Music : 
♪ YouTube Music : https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=Ms1EsS1D0lQ&si=4ah6c0NhQtX4o-75
♪ Hungama : 
♪ Resso : https://www.resso.com/album/7316642223532148738?

Lyrics - 
लड़का:- धीरे धीरे जान अनजान होत बाड़ू
मरता लईका सेयान होत बाड़ू
बोल सेनुर बनब की सिंगारे रहब
लड़की:- जब तक जियब तोहारे रहब...
शादी तोहसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब....

लड़का:- सब मान जाई ना त जान जाई,ए रानी हो जा तू राजी हो
रहबु कुँआरे ना तोहरा दुआरे जानू हमार बाजा बाजी हो
लड़की:- कबो छोड़ब ना वादा ना तोड़ब ए जान तनि हमरा प राख भरोसा
बानी लाइल तू खा ल ना डोसा ए जान मुँह कर ना जइसे समोसा

लड़का:- कर ना हद,बड़ी होता दरद, बोल मरद बनब की ईयारे रहब
लड़की:- जब तक जियब तोहारे रहब...
शादी तोहसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब....
पापाजी के भले दुआरे रहब शादी तोसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब


लड़का :- छूटी ना प्यार परिवार भले छूटी,देखब के हमरा के बोली हो
क ल सगाई तबे तोहार आई,नीलकमल घरे डोली हो

लड़की :- काहे मनवा में फूट ता लावा, ई मोहब्बत प बा तोहरे दावा
मिली आशु दिल मे ना में जगह, केहू आई ना तोहरा अलावा
लड़का :- जवने ही रात, कह आई बारात, मयूर बान्हि खड़ा अपना कपारे रहब

लड़की :- जब तक जियब तोहारे रहब...
शादी तोहसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब....
पापाजी के भले दुआरे रहब शादी तोसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब

#KuwareRahab #NeelkamalSingh #BhojpuriSong 
#NewSong #ShilpiRaj #NeelamGiri #bhojpurisong

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | Bandhi Muthi Lakh Ni Kholi To Kakh Ni | Gujarati New Song 2023 | ગુજરાતી ગીત

જાઓ રાકેશ બારોટનું નવું ગુજરાતી ગીત માટે તૈયાર થઈ "બાંધી મુઠી લાખની ખોલી તો ખાખની" માત્ર @SaregamaGujarati પર 💜

Listen to the best of Rakesh Barot songs only on Saregama Gujarati !
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLUzteH3czVO5WMxyPrP2RWK4MMHuCKLwL

Lyrics
એ મહેમાનગતિ જ્યોતો હું ભાઇભાધં હારે ઓટો
એ ઘર માંદીવાલ ઉપર જોયો એના જેવો ફોટો
એ કાળજા કકળી ઉઠ્યા જોયી દીવાલ માથેફોટો
એ જોતો તો ફોટો એ તો ભરી નેઆયી લોટો
બોધી મઠુ ી હતી લાખની મારી બોધી મઠુ ી હતી લાખની...(2)
એ બોધી મઠુ ી હતી લાખની મારી બોધી મઠુ ી હતી લાખની
ખલુ ી મઠુ ી ને ખબર પડી થઇ જય એ તો ખાખ ની
એ ખલુ ી મઠુ ી ને ખબર પડી થઇ જય હાવ ખાખ ની
એ જરૂર હતી જીવનભર માટેમારા એના સાથની
ચમ જતી રઈ ગોંડી ખબર ના પડી એ વાત ની
એ પછી મહમે ાનગતિ જ્યોતો હું ભાઇભાધં હારે ઓટો
એ ઘર માંદીવાલ ઉપર જોયો એના જેવો ફોટો
એ કાળજા કકળી ઉઠ્યા જોયી દીવાલ માથેફોટો

In this video by Dhruv Rathee, the focus is on the heart-wrenching story of illegal immigration from India, specifically the tragic journey of a family from the small village of Dingucha, Gujarat. The video delves into the realities of "donkey flights," a term for illegal immigration routes, and the dangerous journeys families undertake for a better life in countries like the USA ,UK and Canada. snippet.title: തിരുവാതിര പുണ്യം നേടിത്തരുന്ന ശിവപാർവ്വതിയുടെ പുണ്യഗാനങ്ങൾ | Thiruvathira #shiva #shivaparvati #2023
snippet.description:
തിരുവാതിര പുണ്യം നേടിത്തരുന്ന ശിവപാർവ്വതിയുടെ പുണ്യഗാനങ്ങൾ | Thiruvathira #shiva #shivaparvati #thiruvaethirva #2023 

Thiruvathira is a Hindu festival which is celebrated on Thiruvathira Nakshatra in the malayalam Month of Dhanu.Thiruvathira is the night of Makairam Nakshatra and Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is the most famous temple during the Dhanumasa Thiruvathira festival. Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is also known as the Sabarimala of women, enshrining Lord Shiva and Parvati. Although the deities of Lord Shiva and Parvati are in the same shrine, both of them face different directions. Shiva faces east and Parvati faces west.The Nata of Goddess Parvathi in Thiruvairanikulam temple is opened in Thiruvathira in the month of Dhanu.Thiruvathirakali or Kaikottikali is a unique dance performed in Kerala on the auspicious day of Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.As per Hindu mythology, this dance is what brought Kamadeva (God of Love) back to life when he had been burnt to ashes by Lord Shiva's fury.According to Hindu belief that,Lord Shiva agreed to marry Goddess Parvati as a result of severe penance on Thiruvathira. It is believed that observing Dhanumasa Tiruvathira vratam according to fate will bring prosperity, long sumangaliyoga and happy married life.

localized.title: തിരുവാതിര പുണ്യം നേടിത്തരുന്ന ശിവപാർവ്വതിയുടെ പുണ്യഗാനങ്ങൾ | Thiruvathira #shiva #shivaparvati #2023
localized.description:
തിരുവാതിര പുണ്യം നേടിത്തരുന്ന ശിവപാർവ്വതിയുടെ പുണ്യഗാനങ്ങൾ | Thiruvathira #shiva #shivaparvati #thiruvaethirva #2023 

Thiruvathira is a Hindu festival which is celebrated on Thiruvathira Nakshatra in the malayalam Month of Dhanu.Thiruvathira is the night of Makairam Nakshatra and Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is the most famous temple during the Dhanumasa Thiruvathira festival. Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is also known as the Sabarimala of women, enshrining Lord Shiva and Parvati. Although the deities of Lord Shiva and Parvati are in the same shrine, both of them face different directions. Shiva faces east and Parvati faces west.The Nata of Goddess Parvathi in Thiruvairanikulam temple is opened in Thiruvathira in the month of Dhanu.Thiruvathirakali or Kaikottikali is a unique dance performed in Kerala on the auspicious day of Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.As per Hindu mythology, this dance is what brought Kamadeva (God of Love) back to life when he had been burnt to ashes by Lord Shiva's fury.According to Hindu belief that,Lord Shiva agreed to marry Goddess Parvati as a result of severe penance on Thiruvathira. It is believed that observing Dhanumasa Tiruvathira vratam according to fate will bring prosperity, long sumangaliyoga and happy married life.

snippet.description:
Coming on January 1st! New Card Type! 
Introducing an all new strategy element to Clash Royale!
Change your defence with the first new Tower Troop, The Cannoneer! 
Blast the attacking troops away with Cannoneer's massive cannon! Boom!
More Tower Troops to come soon...

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale

In this uproarious video, we follow a middle-class family as they embark on a memorable journey to an upscale restaurant to celebrate Mom's birthday. Watch as they navigate the uncharted waters of fine dining, leading to a series of comical misadventures.

snippet.title: SURPRISE DATE WITH A FAN GIRL 😍 | MOHAK NARANG
snippet.description:
You can buy this Garnier Vitamin C range from here:
https://bit.ly/3sABpsU
@garnierindia

Hi guys, hope you are doing well. 
Looking for ways to flaunt the healthy skin of your dreams this festive season? In today’s video, I’m going to reveal how to achieve spotless, bright skin in three simple steps by using Garnier vitamin C skincare products. So, without further ado, let’s get started. 

Vitamin C, being one of the most effective ingredients in the skincare industry, offers a variety of benefits to the skin. And to make the most of this ingredient, it’s crucial to include it in your skincare routine, be it as a cleanser, serum, moisturiser or more, especially when the festive season is here. So, to help you flaunt spotless, bright skin and prep it for the festive season, here’s a simple yet super effective 3-step skincare regimen to cleanse, treat and seal moisture in your skin effortlessly – 

Step 1: Start by cleansing your face with the Garnier Bright Complete Face Wash to get rid of dirt, dust, oil, sebum, and impurities. Apply the face wash on wet face and massage gently, avoiding the eye contour area. The vitamin C face wash helps reduce dullness and restore your glowing, healthy-looking complexion. It also helps lessen dark spots and acne marks in just a few days, while leaving the skin feel bright. The Garnier Vitamin C face wash is gentle on the skin and suitable for all skin types. 

Step 2: Next, using the dropper take out a pea-sized amount of the Garnier Vitamin C Serum and apply it on cleansed skin. Dab the Garnier face serum all over your face and neck using small, gentle tapping motions. Enriched with 30X vitamin C, the Garnier serum fades dark spots and dull skin in just three days. It is made with a combination of vitamin C, niacinamide and salicylic acid to give your skin an instant boost of freshness and brightness. The lightweight and non-oily formula instantly penetrates the skin and makes it feel super comfortable all day long. The vitamin C face serum is available in four different sizes for you to choose from and is formulated without sulphates and parabens. 

Step 3: Finish off your three-step vitamin C routine by applying the Garnier Bright Complete Serum Cream evenly on your face and neck. The Garnier Serum Cream is made with a two-in-one formulation that helps you achieve the best of both worlds. It easily penetrates the deepest level of the skin and shields it from signs of sun damage such as skin tanning, dark spots, and sunburn. This cream also lightens dark spots, brightens skin, and evens skin tone. 

These products are definitely a game-changer for me. Highly recommended! So, what are you waiting for? Grab your hands on the Garnier vitamin C skincare products right away to #CleanseTreatSeal your skin on the go this festive season. 

I hope you found this video helpful and if you did, don’t forget to like, share, and subscribe to my channel for more such videos. Also, let me know your thoughts in the comments below.  
Thank you for watching, see you soon!

snippet.title: Recipe 795;: Thuruvathirai Arudra
snippet.description:
Arudra Darshan is a Tamil festival and this day is dedicated to Lord Shiva. Arudra Nakshatram, which is also known as Thiruvaathirai Nakshatram, during Maargazhi Masam is considered highly auspicious. On this day Arudra Nakshatra also coincides with Pournami.

On this day Nataraj form of Lord Shiva is worshipped during Arunodaya along with holy chanting from Vedas. Being dedicated to Nataraj form of Lord Shiva this day is also considered as the birthday of Lord Shiva. In rest of the India it is Maha Shivaratri which is considered as the birthday of Lord Shiva.

So on this special occasion sending across a video of the recipe that is usually done on Thiruvathirai. 

Kindly have a look at the  Ingredients and recipe ; 

#Ingredients

#Kali

Raw Rice - 1 cup
Moong Dal - 1 tsp
Jaggery - 2 cup
Water - 3 cup
Cardamom Powder - 1/2 tsp
Grated Coconut - 4 to 5 spoon
Ghee - 4 spoon & Cashew Nuts

#7Kaai_Kootu

Ash gourd
Pumpkin
Broad Beans
Carrot
Yam
Raw Banana
Sweet Potato
Toor Dal - 2 tbsp
Oil - 7 spoon
Coriander Seeds - 3 spoon
Gram dal - 3 tsp
Pepepr Seeds - 1/2 tsp
Fenugreek - 1/4 tsp
Dry Chilli - 15 nos
Grated Coconut - 1/2
Curry Leaves
Lima Beans
Asafoetida - 4 piece
Water - 1 cup
Salt - 1 tsp
Turmeric Powder - 1/2 tsp
Curry Leaves
Jaggery small piece
Boiled Toor Dal - 4 tbsp
Mustard Seeds - 1 tsp
Dry Chilli - 3 nos

At the Gokuldham Society, Sodhi and Roshan lavishly celebrate their wedding anniversary. The gathering is enjoyed by all Gokuldham inhabitants, with Tapu Sena receiving credit for the decoration. Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in the soul-stirring melodies of "Desh Pehle," a heartfelt tribute to the spirit of patriotism. Song out now on Hitz Music.

Vinod Bhanushali presents, Main ATAL Hoon, starring Pankaj Tripathi, directed by Ravi Jadhav, is written by Rishi Virmani and Ravi Jadhav. A Bhanushali Studios Limited and Legend Studios production, the film is produced by Vinod Bhanushali, Sandeep Singh, and Kamlesh Bhanushali.
The film releases on 19th January 2024 in cinemas near you. 

Stream the song here - https://bfan.link/desh-pehle

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 10 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 23rd December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

snippet.title: DIVINE - 4.10 | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
Download & Stream: https://lnk.to/4.10

Crafted against the evocative backdrop of a sampled melody from the legendary Punjabi singer Laal Chand Yamla Jatt, this musical masterpiece vividly depicts DIVINE's innermost thoughts and emotions. Produced by the duo Zzorawar and Arsh Heer, the beats resonate with the hauntingly beautiful verses of Yamla Jatt's classic, 'Tere Ni Karara Mainu Puteya,Das Main Ki Pyar Wichon Kuhteya' which translates to 'Your promises cost me dearly, tell me what did I gain from love.' This sample threads through the rhythm, infusing the track with an emotional depth that perfectly aligns with DIVINE's lyrical narrative.

Audio Credits:

Written and Performed by: DIVINE, Lal Chand Yamla Jatt
Produced by: ZZORAWAR, Arsh Heer
Mixed & Mastered by: Hanish Taneja

snippet.title: Our Christmas Eve celebration in London/அனைவருக்கும் கிறிஸ்மஸ் நல் வாழ்த்துக்கள்.. Merry Christmas🎄
snippet.description:
In this video I have showed how we celebrate Christmas Eve at my home in London.
Christmas is an annual festival commemorating the birth of Jesus Christ, observed primarily on December 25 as a religious and cultural celebration among billions of people around the world.A feast central to the liturgical year in Christianity, it follows the season of Advent (which begins four Sundays before) or the Nativity Fast, and initiates the season of Christmastide, which historically in the West lasts twelve days and culminates on Twelfth Night.Christmas Day is a public holiday in many countries,is celebrated religiously by a majority of Christians,as well as culturally by many non-Christians,and forms an integral part of the holiday season surrounding it.

snippet.title: নারু গোপাল | Gopal Bhar | Episode - 1013
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1


The Nawab wants to go to Krishnanager and make a mockery of Gopal. Meanwhile, Maharaj and all the members of the court go to Montri's house for a feast but Gopal eats all the sweets. How will Montri react to this?


Show Name: Gopal Bhar
Episode No: 1013

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #গোপালভর 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

Click to watch all the episodes of Gopal Bhar -
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5O3zv2ZcASiKOTRSEBzEwxlnw10AkNbE

snippet.description:

Mannat Murad Episode 26 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by PEL - 25th December 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Presented by PEL

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 09 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 22nd December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

snippet.title: Main ATAL Hoon - Trailer | Pankaj Tripathi | Ravi Jadhav | Vinod Bhanushali | 19 Jan 2024
snippet.description:
More than a poet. More than a statesman. More than a Prime Minister. Presenting the trailer of #MainATALHoon. 

Vinod Bhanushali presents, Main ATAL Hoon, a film on the extraordinary life of the leader you knew but the man you didn't, starring National Award winner Pankaj Tripathi. 

Directed by National Awardee Ravi Jadhav, and written by Rishi Virmani and Ravi Jadhav, "Main ATAL Hoon" presented by Bhanushali Studios Limited and Legend Studios, is produced by Vinod Bhanushali, Sandeep Singh, and Kamlesh Bhanushali.
The film releases on 19th January 2024 in cinemas near you. 


CREDITS:

Starring : Pankaj Tripathi

snippet.title: Popatlal है Taarak का 'Favorite Uncle' |Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah |Giggles At Gada Electronics
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Jetha comes to the soda shop and asks Abdul to serve double soda to everyone. Taarak asks him if there is any special occasion but he says that Tapu has been studying the whole day. Bhide and Sodhi join him too as they share that their kids are doing the same too. Later, Tapu Sena feels guilty of hiding their suspension from their parents.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1077
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2023 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Why RICH people wants to look POOR | Strange secrets of RICH | GIGL
snippet.description:
Why RICH people wants to look POOR | Strange secrets of RICH | GIGL

In short hamne is video me human psychology ke 3 amazing concepts ke baare me seekha pehla concept tha:- 

“Social proof in tribes” yaani ki agar ek ameer insaan ke normal customers hai aur vo unhi ki tarah deekhega to relatibility ke principle ke according log us ke saath zaada connect karenge jis se trust create hoga aur finally sales badegi. Is par detal me ek book hai Dr robert cialidini ki jiska naam hai “influence the psychology of persuasion” . jise aap chahe to gigl app me free me hindi me sun sakte hai. Iska link mein description aur first comment me de dunga.

Next concept tha “Normal life style and being part of tribe” jisme hamne aman goel ka case dekha ki kaise vo simple hi rehna chahte hai kyunki 1) unhe ye life style pasand hai 2) unke jo saath wale log hai vo bhi unhe usi tareeke se dekhe jaise vo apne startup ko bechne se pehle dikhte the.

Next concept hamne seekha “maslow pyramid” jo ki human needs ke baare me batata hai ki kayi ameer logo ko bilkul fark nhi padta ki aur log kya soch rahe hai ya unhe bhaut ache kapde pehnne hai kyunki vo self actualization wale stage me phunch chuka hai.

In short … do type ke ameer hai dono simple dress karne ki koshish kar rahe hai.. Ek apni sales badhana chahta hai aur ek khud ko apne kaam se express karna chahta hai.

I hope ye video aapko achi lagi nogi.

Jai Hind

🌟 Get ready for a laughter-packed rollercoaster ride with the dazzling and delightful Jasmine Bhasin in our latest podcast episode! 🎙️ Known for her incredible performances on TV and in Punjabi films, Jasmine skyrocketed to fame after winning hearts on the reality show Bigg Boss. 🏆

Join us as we dive deep into the world of this talented Indian celebrity, discussing her journey, behind-the-scenes anecdotes, and the hilarious moments that make her the queen of entertainment! 👑 From her charismatic presence on the small screen to her blockbuster ventures in Punjabi cinema, Jasmine spills the beans on it all.

Expect laughs, candid conversations, and a whole lot of masti as Jasmine takes us on a journey through her career, life, and everything in between. 🤣 Don't miss out on the inside scoop and join the party by hitting that play button now!

snippet.title: Visiting the Closest Town to Space (Life with 50% less oxygen)
snippet.description:
Subscribe ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn
La Rinconada, the closest inhabited place to the sky on Earth, where people are living above the clouds.

At this extreme altitude of 5,100 meters, the atmosphere significantly thins and the locals are living with only  50% of the usual oxygen levels. Their bodies have evolved to produce two times more blood cells than ours. On this barren land, not even a single tree can survive because of the low air pressure. 

This town in the Peruvian Andes is even 300 meters higher than Mont Blanc, the highest peak in the Alps of Europe. 
 
Far from the modern world, it is a place where crime and danger are always nearby.  People come to these harsh lands for only one reason: gold. About 50,000 people have settled here, among piles of trash, all dreaming of wealth.

id.title: Mengunjungi Kota Terdekat ke Luar Angkasa (Kehidupan dengan oksigen 50% lebih rendah)
id.description:
La Rinconada, tempat berpenghuni yang paling dekat dengan langit di Bumi, tempat manusia tinggal di atas awan.

Pada ketinggian ekstrem 5.100 meter ini, atmosfer menipis secara signifikan dan penduduk setempat hidup dengan hanya 50% dari tingkat oksigen biasanya. Tubuh mereka telah berevolusi untuk menghasilkan sel darah dua kali lebih banyak daripada tubuh kita. Di tanah tandus ini, tidak ada satu pohon pun yang mampu bertahan karena rendahnya tekanan udara.

Kota di Andes Peru ini bahkan lebih tinggi 300 meter dari Mont Blanc, puncak tertinggi di Pegunungan Alpen Eropa.
 
Jauh dari dunia modern, ini adalah tempat dimana kejahatan dan bahaya selalu ada di dekatnya. Orang-orang datang ke negeri yang keras ini hanya karena satu alasan: emas. Sekitar 50.000 orang menetap di sini, di antara tumpukan sampah, semuanya memimpikan kekayaan.

hi.title: Space ke sabse nazdeeki Sheher ki Yatra (50% kam oxygen ke saath zindagi)
hi.description:
Subscribe karen ►  https://goo.gl/MKi8tn
La Rinakonaada, prthvee par aakaash ke sabase nikat nivaas sthaan hai, jahaan log baadalon ke oopar rah rahe hain.

5,100 meetar kee is charam oonchaee par, vaataavaran kaaphee patala ho gaya hai aur sthaaneey log saamaany okseejan star ke keval 50% ke saath rah rahe hain. Unake shareer hamaaree tulana mein do guna adhik rakt koshikaon ka utpaadan karane ke lie vikasit hue hain. Is banjar bhoomi par vaayudaab kam hone ke kaaran ek bhee ped jeevit nahin rah paata.

Peroo ke endeej ka yah shahar yoorop ke aalps kee sabase oonchee chotee mont blaink se bhee 300 meetar ooncha hai.
 
Aadhunik duniya se door, yah ek aisee jagah hai jahaan aparaadh aur khatara hamesha aasapaas rahata hai. Log in kathor bhoomiyon par keval ek hee kaaran se aate hain: sona. Yahaan koode ke dher ke beech kareeb 50,000 log bas gae hain, sabhee daulat ka sapana dekh rahe hain.

Far from the modern world, it is a place where crime and danger are always nearby.  People come to these harsh lands for only one reason: gold. About 50,000 people have settled here, among piles of trash, all dreaming of wealth.

fr.title: Visiter la ville la plus proche de l'espace (Vivre avec 50% d'oxygène en moins)
fr.description:
La Rinconada, l'endroit habité le plus proche du ciel sur Terre, où les gens vivent au-dessus des nuages.

À cette altitude extrême de 5 100 mètres, l’atmosphère s’amincit considérablement et les habitants vivent avec seulement 50 % des niveaux d’oxygène habituels. Leur corps a évolué pour produire deux fois plus de cellules sanguines que le nôtre. Sur cette terre aride, pas un seul arbre ne peut survivre à cause de la faible pression atmosphérique.

Cette ville des Andes péruviennes culmine même à 300 mètres au-dessus du Mont Blanc, le plus haut sommet des Alpes d'Europe.
 
Loin du monde moderne, c'est un endroit où le crime et le danger sont toujours proches. Les gens viennent dans ces terres difficiles pour une seule raison : l’or. Environ 50 000 personnes se sont installées ici, parmi des tas d’ordures, rêvant toutes de richesse.

es.description:
La Rinconada, el lugar habitado más cercano al cielo en la Tierra, donde la gente vive por encima de las nubes.

A esta altitud extrema de 5.100 metros, la atmósfera se adelgaza considerablemente y los lugareños viven con sólo el 50% de los niveles habituales de oxígeno. Sus cuerpos han evolucionado para producir dos veces más células sanguíneas que el nuestro. En esta tierra árida, ni siquiera un solo árbol puede sobrevivir debido a la baja presión del aire.

Este pueblo de los Andes peruanos está incluso 300 metros más alto que el Mont Blanc, el pico más alto de los Alpes de Europa.
 
Lejos del mundo moderno, es un lugar donde el crimen y el peligro siempre están cerca. La gente viene a estas duras tierras por una sola razón: el oro. Unas 50.000 personas se han asentado aquí, entre montones de basura, todos soñando con la riqueza.

ko.title: 우주에서 가장 가까운 마을을 방문하기 (산소 50% 더 적은 생활)
ko.description:
지구상에서 하늘과 가장 가까운 사람이 사는 곳, 구름 위에서 사람들이 살고 있는 라 링코나다.

5,100미터에 달하는 이 극단적인 고도에서는 대기가 상당히 얇아지고 현지인들은 평소 산소 수준의 50%만 생활하고 있습니다. 그들의 몸은 우리 몸보다 두 배 더 많은 혈액 세포를 생산하도록 진화했습니다. 이 척박한 땅에는 낮은 기압 때문에 나무 한 그루도 살 수 없습니다.

페루 안데스 산맥에 위치한 이 마을은 유럽 알프스의 최고봉인 몽블랑보다 무려 300m 더 높습니다.
 
현대사회와는 거리가 멀고, 범죄와 위험이 늘 가까이 있는 곳입니다. 사람들이 이 험난한 땅에 오는 이유는 단 하나, 바로 금입니다. 약 5만 명의 사람들이 쓰레기 더미 속에서 부를 꿈꾸며 이곳에 정착했습니다.

bn.description:
"লা রিনকোনাডা, পৃথিবীর আকাশের সবচেয়ে কাছের জনবসতিপূর্ণ স্থান, যেখানে মানুষ মেঘের উপরে বাস করে।

5,100 মিটারের এই চরম উচ্চতায়, বায়ুমণ্ডল উল্লেখযোগ্যভাবে পাতলা এবং স্থানীয়রা স্বাভাবিক অক্সিজেনের মাত্রার মাত্র 50% নিয়ে বসবাস করছে। তাদের শরীর আমাদের চেয়ে দুইগুণ বেশি রক্তকণিকা তৈরি করতে বিবর্তিত হয়েছে। এই অনুর্বর জমিতে বাতাসের চাপ কম থাকায় একটি গাছও বাঁচতে পারে না।

পেরুভিয়ান আন্দিজের এই শহরটি ইউরোপের আল্পসের সর্বোচ্চ শৃঙ্গ মন্ট ব্ল্যাঙ্কের থেকেও 300 মিটার উঁচু।
 
আধুনিক বিশ্ব থেকে দূরে, এটি এমন একটি জায়গা যেখানে অপরাধ এবং বিপদ সবসময় কাছাকাছি থাকে। মানুষ শুধুমাত্র একটি কারণে এই কঠোর জমিতে আসে: সোনা। প্রায় 50,000 মানুষ এখানে বসতি স্থাপন করেছে, আবর্জনার স্তূপের মধ্যে, সবাই সম্পদের স্বপ্ন দেখছে।

ru.title: Посещение ближайшего к космосу города (Жизнь с 50% дефицитом кислорода)
ru.description:
Ла-Ринконада, самое близкое к небу населенное место на Земле, где люди живут над облаками.

На этой экстремальной высоте в 5100 метров атмосфера значительно разрежается, и местные жители живут только с 50% обычного уровня кислорода. Их тела эволюционировали, чтобы производить в два раза больше клеток крови, чем наши. На этой бесплодной земле не может выжить ни одно дерево из-за низкого давления воздуха.

Этот город в перуанских Андах даже на 300 метров выше Монблана, самой высокой вершины Альп Европы.
 
Вдали от современного мира, это место, где преступность и опасность всегда рядом. Люди приезжают в эти суровые края только по одной причине: золото. Здесь, среди груд мусора, поселилось около 50 000 человек, мечтающих о богатстве.

tr.title: Uzaya En Yakın Yerleşim Yerine Yolculuk (%50 az oksijen ile yaşam)
tr.description:
Abone olabilirsiniz ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn
La Rinconada, insanların bulutların üzerinde yaşadığı, gökyüzüne en yakın yerleşim yeri. 

5100 metrelik bu son derece yüksek rakımda, atmosfer önemli ölçüde inceliyor ve yerel halk normal oksijen seviyesinin sadece yarısıyla yaşıyor. Vücutları, bizimkinden iki kat daha fazla kan hücresi üretmek üzere adapte olmuş. Düşük hava basıncı nedeniyle çoraklaşan bu topraklarda hiçbir ağaç hayatta kalamıyor. 
 
Peru’nun And Dağlarında bulunan bu kasaba, Avrupa Alpleri’nin en yüksek zirvesi Mont Blanc’tan bile 300 metre daha yüksekte. 

Modern dünyadan uzakta, suç ve tehlikenin kol gezdiği bu zorlu topraklara insanların gelmesinin yalnızca bir nedeni var: altın. Buraya yerleşen yaklaşık 50.000 kişi, çöp yığınlarının arasında bir gün zengin olma umuduyla yaşıyor.

ar.title: زيارة أقرب بلدة للفضاء (الحياة مع 50% فقط من الأكسجين)
ar.description:
لا رينكونادا، أقرب مكان مأهول إلى السماء على الأرض، حيث يعيش الناس فوق السحاب.

على هذا الارتفاع البالغ 5100 متر، يصبح الغلاف الجوي أقل كثافة بشكل ملحوظ ويعيش السكان المحليون مع 50% فقط من مستويات الأكسجين المعتادة. لقد تطورت أجسامهم لتنتج خلايا دم أكثر بمرتين من خلايانا. في هذه الأرض القاحلة، لا يمكن لشجرة واحدة أن تبقى على قيد الحياة بسبب انخفاض ضغط الهواء.

تقع هذه المدينة الواقعة في جبال الأنديز في بيرو على ارتفاع 300 متر عن مونت بلانك، أعلى قمة في جبال الألب في أوروبا.
 
بعيدًا عن العالم الحديث، فهو مكان تتواجد فيه الجريمة والخطر دائمًا في مكان قريب. يأتي الناس إلى هذه الأراضي القاسية لسبب واحد فقط: الذهب. لقد استقر هنا حوالي 50 ألف شخص، بين أكوام القمامة، وكلهم يحلمون بالثروة.

ur.title: خلا کے قریب ترین واقع قصبے (50 فیصد کم آکسیجن کے ساتھ زندگی)
ur.description:
لا رنکوناڈا، زمین پر آسمان کے قریب ترین آباد مقام، جہاں لوگ بادلوں کے اوپر رہ رہے ہیں۔

5,100 میٹر کی اس انتہائی اونچائی پر، ماحول نمایاں طور پر پتلا ہے اور مقامی لوگ صرف 50 فیصد آکسیجن لیول کے ساتھ رہ رہے ہیں۔ ان کے جسم نے ہمارے جسم سے دو گنا زیادہ خون کے خلیات تیار کیے ہیں۔ اس بنجر زمین پر ہوا کے کم دباؤ کی وجہ سے ایک درخت بھی زندہ نہیں رہ سکتا۔

پیرو اینڈیز میں واقع یہ قصبہ یورپ کے الپس کی بلند ترین چوٹی مونٹ بلانک سے بھی 300 میٹر بلند ہے۔
 
جدید دنیا سے دور، یہ ایک ایسی جگہ ہے جہاں جرم اور خطرہ ہمیشہ قریب ہی رہتے ہیں۔ لوگ ان سخت زمینوں پر صرف ایک وجہ سے آتے ہیں: سونا۔ یہاں تقریباً 50,000 لوگ آباد ہیں، کچرے کے ڈھیروں کے درمیان، سب دولت کے خواب دیکھ رہے ہیں۔

it.title: Visitare la Città più vicina allo Spazio (Vita con il 50% di Ossigeno in meno)
it.description:
La Rinconada, il luogo abitato più vicino al cielo sulla Terra, dove le persone vivono sopra le nuvole.

A questa altitudine estrema di 5.100 metri, l'atmosfera si assottiglia notevolmente e la gente del posto vive con solo il 50% del normale livello di ossigeno. I loro corpi si sono evoluti per produrre due volte più cellule del sangue delle nostre. Su questa terra arida nemmeno un singolo albero può sopravvivere a causa della bassa pressione atmosferica.

Questa città delle Ande peruviane è addirittura 300 metri più alta del Monte Bianco, la vetta più alta delle Alpi d'Europa.
 
Lontano dal mondo moderno, è un luogo dove la criminalità e il pericolo sono sempre vicini. Le persone vengono in queste terre aspre per una sola ragione: l'oro. Qui, tra cumuli di spazzatura, si sono stabilite circa 50.000 persone, tutte sognanti la ricchezza.

de.title: Besuch der dem Weltall am dichtesten gelegenen Stadt (Leben mit 50% Sauerstoff)
de.description:
La Rinconada, der dem Himmel am nächsten gelegene bewohnte Ort auf der Erde, wo Menschen über den Wolken leben.

In dieser extremen Höhe von 5.100 Metern wird die Atmosphäre deutlich dünner und die Einheimischen leben mit nur 50 % des üblichen Sauerstoffgehalts. Ihr Körper hat sich so entwickelt, dass er doppelt so viele Blutzellen produziert wie unserer. Auf diesem kargen Land kann aufgrund des niedrigen Luftdrucks nicht einmal ein einziger Baum überleben.

Diese Stadt in den peruanischen Anden ist sogar 300 Meter höher als der Mont Blanc, der höchste Berg der Alpen Europas.
 
Weit entfernt von der modernen Welt ist es ein Ort, an dem Kriminalität und Gefahr immer in der Nähe sind. Die Menschen kommen nur aus einem Grund in diese rauen Länder: Gold. Etwa 50.000 Menschen haben sich hier inmitten von Müllbergen niedergelassen und träumen alle vom Reichtum.

ja.title: 宇宙に一番近い街への旅 (酸素が50％も少ない中での生活)
ja.description:
地球上で空に最も近い人が住む場所、ラ リンコナダ。人々は雲の上で暮らしています。

高度 5,100 メートルのこの極度の場所では、大気は著しく薄くなり、地元住民は通常の酸素レベルの 50% のみで生活しています。 彼らの体は、私たちの体よりも 2 倍多くの血球を生成するように進化しました。 この不毛の地では、低気圧のせいで木一本も生き残ることができません。

ペルーのアンデス山脈にあるこの町は、ヨーロッパのアルプス最高峰であるモンブランよりも 300 メートルも高いところにあります。
 
現代とは程遠い、犯罪と危険が常に隣り合わせの場所。 人々がこの過酷な土地にやってくる理由はただ一つ、それは金です。 約5万人がここに定住し、ゴミの山に囲まれながら富を夢見ている。
